OL,3,CVolunteer traders give Rotherham girl
OL,4,Cwith Batten disease #100k home
OL,5,Crenovation
OL,7,FVolunteer tradesmen have carried out a
OL,8,F#100,000 home renovation to help a
OL,9,Fblind girl with an incurable disease
OL,10,Flive more comfortably.
OL,12,FThe degenerative condition can lead to
OL,13,Fseizures, blindness and childhood
OL,14,Fdementia.
OL,16,FStevie's father, Paul, started trying
OL,17,Fto create a home able to meet his
OL,18,Fdaughter's long-term needs two years
OL,19,Fago, but costs quickly spiralled.
