OL,3,CVolunteer traders give Rotherham girl
OL,4,Cwith Batten disease #100k home
OL,5,Crenovation
OL,7,FAfter hearing their story, the
OL,8,Fcommunity rallied around to make the
OL,9,Fproperty in Wath upon Dearne more safe
OL,10,Fand accessible.
OL,12,FMr Taylor told ITV News: "I can't
OL,13,Fthank everyone enough. I've lived here
OL,14,Fall my life and it's a place where
OL,15,Fpeople look out for each other.
OL,17,F"All these things have been achieved
OL,18,Fbecause of what people have done for
OL,19,Fus. You can't put that into words. You
OL,20,Fcan't measure it."
