OL,4,Cwith Batten disease #100k home
OL,5,Crenovation
OL,7,FAround 40 tradespeople inspired by
OL,8,FStevie's story stepped in, donating
OL,9,Ftime and materials which Paul believes
OL,10,Fhas saved the family at least #100,000.
OL,12,FMr Taylor said: "I always worried at
OL,13,Fnight if I heard her get up for the
OL,14,Ftoilet that she was going to turn the
OL,15,Fwrong way and fall down the stairs.
OL,17,F"To have her bed and bathroom on the
OL,18,Fsame level and somewhere we can sleep,
OL,19,Fso we can hear her in the night, has
OL,20,Fbeen a major thing. It's helped us all
OL,21,Frelax a bit more."
