OL,7,FStevie, who has been described as
OL,8,F"bright" and "bubbly" by her father,
OL,9,Falso thanked the community for
OL,10,Fcreating her dream bedroom.
OL,12,FShe added: "It's nice to know people
OL,13,Fwant to help us and put time and
OL,14,Feffort into making the house look
OL,15,Fnice."
OL,17,FBatten disease is a group of incurable
OL,18,Fgenetic disorders. There are 13 known
OL,19,Ftypes.
