OL,7,FPassed down through families, it
OL,8,Fresults from a genetic mutation.
OL,10,FThe disorder affects cells' ability to
OL,11,Fbreak down and get rid of cellular
OL,12,Fwaste, causing problems with the
OL,13,Fnervous system.
OL,15,FSymptoms, which can appear in
OL,16,Fchildhood and early adulthood, include
OL,17,Fseizures, vision loss and cognitive
OL,18,Fproblems.
