OL,7,FHealthcare providers estimate that
OL,8,FBatten disease affects about one in
OL,9,Fevery 25,000 babies.
OL,11,FSiblings of children with Batten
OL,12,Fdisease have a 25% chance of having
OL,13,Fthe disorder.
OL,15,FCurrently, there is only a treatment
OL,16,Favailable for one form of Batten
OL,17,Fdisease and there is no cure.
