OL,7,FLiz Brownnutt, chief executive of
OL,8,FBatten Disease Family Association,
OL,9,Fsaid: "We ned to raise more awareness
OL,10,Fboth with the general public as well
OL,11,Fas the medical profession because we
OL,12,Fneed more treatments.
OL,14,F"We really need a quicker path to
OL,15,Fdiagnosis so that more patients can
OL,16,Fget earlier access to treatments and
OL,17,Fultimately help them found a cure."
